markdownRemark.html:
I love es6!

Today I just learned how to build an object with an dynamic key.

function dynamicKey() {
  return 'example';
}

const example = {
  [dynamicKey()]: 'value',
};

frontmatter.title: Build Object with Dynamic Key
frontmatter.description: How to build object with a dynamic key in es6
